Package com.travelportal.model

Model package to manage all the POJO clasess used in SpringMVC

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvailabilityModel
    Model class to manage the availability of a flight according to schedule
    ConnectorFsrModel
    Model class to connect tables: Schedule, Flight, Route, Availability and Deal Created in order to reduce joins and making the primary keys available from one class
    DealModel
    Model class to manage the deals
    FlightModel
    Model class to manage the flight details
    PaymentModel
    Model class to manage the payment details
    RouteModel
    Model class to manage the flight routes
    ScheduleModel
    Model class to manage the schedule of a flight on daily basis including fare,date and time
    TicketModel
    Model class to manage the tickets booked by users
    TravellerModel
    Model class to manage the traveller data insert during ticket booking
    UserModel
    Model class to manage the registered users
